  "prompt": "Where can I learn SAP ABAP in Bangalore with placement?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, several institutes offer SAP ABAP training along with placement assistance. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **SAP Training and Adoption**:\n   - Official SAP training centers offer comprehensive courses on ABAP. Check the SAP website for authorized training centers in Bangalore.\n\n2. **Thinkvidya**:\n   - Platforms like Thinkvidya list various institutes offering SAP ABAP courses. Look for options that mention placement assistance.\n\n3. **Zoom Technologies**:\n   - Known for IT training, Zoom Technologies provides SAP ABAP training with a focus on real-world applications and offers placement support.\n\n4. **Innova IT Technologies**:\n   - This institute offers specialized training in SAP ABAP and has a good reputation for its placement assistance programs.\n\n5. **Softeck**:\n   - Softeck provides training in SAP ABAP and helps with job placements through various industry connections.\n\n6. **Tech Learn Hub**:\n   - They provide comprehensive training in SAP ABAP and often have placement drives for their students.\n\n7. **Oracle Training Institute (OTI)**:\n   - OTI offers a structured approach to learning SAP ABAP and has placement services for graduates.\n\nBefore enrolling, make sure to check reviews, course content, the expertise of trainers, and placement statistics. Additionally, visiting the institutes and speaking to past students can give you a better insight into what to expect.",
